snippet.title: Best VGM 81 - Deep Labyrinth - The Azure Cavern
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 490 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=81-SoTxMmiI

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Deep Labyrinth
The Azure Cavern
